name: Brett (ETH)
description: BRETT is a meme coin based on BRETT character, famously know in the boy's club comics as PEPE's Friend. The oldest launched Brett Token on the ETH Chain. Dogs have had their time and now it's time for Brett to take it from here This is also a community takeover, which means a group of crypto memecoin veterans decided to join forces and take care of the oldest memecoin related to BRETT on ETH. A completely transparent community takeover. By the people, for the people. this coin is not directly related to Matt Furie ( Boys Club)
